  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Think beyond your current life and solve puzzles by coordinating with your past and future lives!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1340310/extras/bdfc4e3080134218c718293b0c817e13.poster.avif?t=1644935009\" width=630 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1340310/extras/bdfc4e3080134218c718293b0c817e13.webm?t=1644935009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1340310/extras/bdfc4e3080134218c718293b0c817e13.mp4?t=1644935009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Encounter all manner of creatures and obstacles that'll have you developing new strategies</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1340310/extras/0abb85841737b575b615bef79b12afc3.poster.avif?t=1644935009\" width=800 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1340310/extras/0abb85841737b575b615bef79b12afc3.webm?t=1644935009\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1340310/extras/0abb85841737b575b615bef79b12afc3.mp4?t=1644935009\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Progress through 9 different areas each adding a new twist.<br></li><li> Solve over 80 puzzles ranging from the very casual to the very challenging.<br></li><li> Use up to 9 lives to help solve increasingly challenging puzzles.<br></li><li> Cute voxel art style with a different theme for each of the nine areas.<br></li><li> Face dangerous thorny plants, catch sneaky rats, drown yourself in rivers and encounter much more as you make your way back to the wold of the living.</li></ul>",
